Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
15 Jul 2024	navbs1	CR 64901 Task 64903: UI - Show Cargo Ids in To Do Complete Thin Client

*/

vars

begin

	self.mnuColumnOrganizer.userObject := table;
